The subtle source-level order issue is not just “what values exist,” it is where the renderer samples them. D3D11 samples the global dot3 state from shader apply and slot0 composition; D3D9 samples selected lights from `drawPrimitive()` immediately before the draw, after the engine has finished staging object state.
